3^{2n}+2^{2m}=5^{2k}
(n,m,k)=(1,2,1)
2^{2m}=5^{2k}-3^{2n}=(5^k-3^n)(5^k+3^n)
5^k-3^n=2^a
5^k+3^n=2^b
a\lt b=2m-a
2\cdot3^n=2^a(2^{b-a}-1)
a=1
3^n=2^{b-a}-1
