3^{2n}=5^{2k}-2^{2m}=(5^k-2^m)(5^k+2^m)
5^k-2^m=3^a
5^k+2^m=3^b
a\lt b=2n-a
2\cdot2^m=3^a(3^{b-1}-1)
a=0
5^k-2^m=1
5^k=2^m+1
3^{2n}=2^{m+1}+1
2^{m+1}=(3^n-1)(3^n+1)
3^n-1=2^a
3^n+1=2^b
a\lt b
2=2^a(2^{b-1}-1)
a=1
